HTML5 Plain Text Editor 
=======================

built with contentediable and HTML5 DOM Ranges

Features:

* Get/Set text

* Set/Get cursor position

* Set/Get selection

* Scroll cursor into view

* Center cursor/selection in view

* Find, Find Next, Find Previous

* Replace, Replace All, Replace in Selection.

* Undo/Redo

* Key shortcuts

* copy/paste

* align left/right and so on

* page breaks